item.description: Returns the number of actual concurrent irods client connections

item.name: yoda.concurrentirodsusers
item.description: Returns the number of unique iRods users that have one or more active connections. (user names with # or space excluded).

item.name: yoda.dailywebdavusers

item.name: yoda.delayedrules.count

item.name: yoda.internalusers.count

item.name: yoda.irodsgroups.count

item.name: yoda.irodsservicecheck
item.description: Returns basic irods server information or connection failure (port 1247) if information could not be retrieved using imisvsvrinfo icommand (local irodsservice not running)

item.name: yoda.listorphanedgroups
item.description: Returns a list of Orphaned Groups An orphaned group is a group that has no groupmanager with a @.uu.nl username.

item.name: yoda.publications.pending[*]
item.description:
Returns the number of publications that should have been published, republished, depublished or updated after a change of the metadata by the datamanager after a number of seconds.
The parameter specifies the number of seconds that publications are considered to be published, depublished, republished of updated (86400 being 1 day)

item.name: yoda.publications.pending[*]
item.description:
Returns the number of publications that should have been published, republished, depublished or updated after a change of the metadata by the datamanager after a number of seconds.
The parameter specifies the number of seconds that publications are considered to be published, depublished, republished of updated (86400 being 1 day)

item.name: yoda.replicationerrors.count
item.description: Returns number of replication errors in the last hour

item.description: for testing purposes. When the parameter in the key is changed, the new value should be returned (this may take several minutes).
